游戏各平台版本都获得评论人的称赞<ref name="mc vita"/><ref name="mc 3ds"/><ref name="mc ps4"/><ref name="mc pc"/>，是[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]2016年评分第二高的PlayStation Vita游戏，仅次于《[[命運石之門0|命運石之門0]]》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/feature/best-videogames-of-2016 |title=The Best Videogames of 2016 |author=Dietz, Jason |date=2016-12-20 |website=Metacritic |publisher=CBS Interactive |access-date=2016-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222041129/http://www.metacritic.com/feature/best-videogames-of-2016 |archive-date=2016-12-22 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。日本上市首周，Vita版销量5375份，3DS版3916份，总计9291份<ref name="jp sales">{{cite web |url=http://gematsu.com/2016/07/media-create-sales-62716-7316 |title=Media Create Sales: 6/27/16 – 7/3/16 |author=Romano, Sal |date=2016-07-06 |work=Gematsu |access-date=2016-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160706133233/http://gematsu.com/2016/07/media-create-sales-62716-7316 |archive-date=2016-07-06 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。 游戏位列2016年6月Vita游戏欧洲销量榜第三位，虽然上市时这个月还有三天就结束<ref>{{cite web |url=https://blog.eu.playstation.com/2016/07/07/battlefield-4-was-the-best-selling-game-on-playstation-store-last-month/ |title=Battlefield 4 was the best-selling game on PlayStation Store last month |author=Dutton, Fred |date=2016-07-07 |website=PlayStation Blog |publisher=Sony Interactive Entertainment |access-date=2016-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160707214351/https://blog.eu.playstation.com/2016/07/07/battlefield-4-was-the-best-selling-game-on-playstation-store-last-month/ |archive-date=2016-07-07 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。Steam版截至2018年7月共收获3.8万名玩家<ref>{{cite web |url=https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2018/07/steam-data-leak-reveals-precise-player-count-for-thousands-of-games/ |title=Valve leaks Steam game player counts; we have the numbers |author=Orland, Kyle |date=2018-07-06 |website=Ars Technica |publisher=Condé Nast |access-date=2018-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180710173043/https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2018/07/steam-data-leak-reveals-precise-player-count-for-thousands-of-games/ |archive-date=2018-07-10 |dead-url=no}} [https://arstechnica.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/games_achievements_players_2018-07-01.csv 完整清单]. {{Webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711204821/https://arstechnica.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/games_achievements_players_2018-07-01.csv |date=2018-07-11}}</ref>。

《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》的四位评论人享受游戏三支队伍的设定及不依时间顺序展开剧情流程，认为这样一来玩家游玩时可以更好理解剧情。其中一人表示了解剧情片段中的事情“很奇妙”，另外他们也喜欢被强调的“人际交往戏份”。另外一人认为“略带嘲笑特性”的对白有助于激励玩家。其中一人表示游戏很有趣，即便是没有玩过系列之前两部作品的玩家也能享受其中<ref name="famitsu review">{{cite magazine |title=ZERO ESCAPE 刻のジレンマ |magazine=Famitsu |publisher=Enterbrain |language=ja |date=2016-06 |issue=1438}}</ref>。他们还认为谜题房间非常有挑战性，很有趣，但希望游戏能为冲着剧情来玩的玩家设置提示功能。其中一位评论人认为玩家有时很难用上道具。他们欣赏谜题房间不像其他密室逃脱游戏那样，给人浅显易懂的感觉<ref name="famitsu review"/>。[[IGN|IGN]]称赞谜题“有创造性”，剧情“精彩”，暗黑基调、决定、结果、“美丽的角色个人时刻”和“晦涩难懂的剧情”很出彩<ref name="ign review"/>。《{{tsl|en|Metro (British newspaper)|地铁报}}》认为剧本很优秀，是他们玩过的最出彩的剧情导向游戏，“电子游戏剧情的里程碑，主题复杂性和决策方面步向新台阶”<ref name="metro"/>。

[[Destructoid|Destructoid]]认为游戏立下了卓越的标准，虽然[[剧情画面|过场动画]]的“糟糕表现”有点煞风景<ref name="destructoid review">{{cite web |url=https://www.destructoid.com/review-zero-time-dilemma-370574.phtml |title=Review: Zero Time Dilemma |author=Andriessen, CJ |date=2016-06-23 |website=Destructoid |publisher=Modern Method |access-date=2017-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160902080500/https://www.destructoid.com/review-zero-time-dilemma-370574.phtml |archive-date=2016-09-02 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。《Fami通》的一位评论人欣赏游戏允许玩家跳过已经看过的过场动画，另一人认为过场动画没能完美对上日本版配音演员的嘴型<ref name="famitsu review"/>。《地铁报》认为“配音质量起伏不定，动画技术非常低”<ref name="metro"/>。

游戏在多个大奖中获奖或被提名，其中赢得[[Destructoid|Destructoid]]的2016年最佳PlayStation Vita游戏奖<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.destructoid.com/destructoid-s-award-for-best-vita-game-of-2016-goes-to--405823.phtml |title=Destructoid's award for Best Vita Game of 2016 goes to... |author=Carter, Chris |date=2016-12-23 |website=Destructoid |publisher=Modern Method |access-date=2017-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170105054751/https://www.destructoid.com/destructoid-s-award-for-best-vita-game-of-2016-goes-to--405823.phtml |archive-date=2017-01-05 |dead-url=no}}</ref>、《[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]》的2016年最佳冒险游戏结局奖<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2017/01/06/2016-adventure-game-awards.aspx?PostPageIndex=2 |page=2 |title=2016 Adventure Game Awards |author=Gwaltney, Javy |date=2017-01-06 |website=Game Informer |publisher=GameStop |access-date=2017-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170112092155/http://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2017/01/06/2016-adventure-game-awards.aspx?PostPageIndex=2 |archive-date=2017-01-12 |dead-url=no}}</ref>和RPGFan读者选择奖的冒险游戏和视觉小说类奖<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rpgfan.com/features/go2016/Category_Awards/Adventure.html |title=Games of the Year 2016: Best Adventure/Visual Novel |date=2017 |work=RPGFan |access-date=2017-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170107154116/http://www.rpgfan.com/features/go2016/Category_Awards/Adventure.html |archive-date=2017-01-07 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏在《Hardcore Gamer》的2016年年度最佳剧情、最佳配音和最佳PlayStation Vita游戏评选中位列第二<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2017/01/01/best-of-2016-day-one-story-soundtrack-voice-acting/241332/ |title=Best of 2016 – Day One: Story, Soundtrack, Voice Acting |date=2017-01-01 |website=Hardcore Gamer |access-date=2017-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170102141708/http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2017/01/01/best-of-2016-day-one-story-soundtrack-voice-acting/241332/ |archive-date=2017-01-02 |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2017/01/07/best-of-2016-day-seven-ps-vita-3ds-artistic-design-technical-graphics/242164/ |title=Best of 2016 – Day Seven: PS Vita, 3DS, Artistic Design, Technical Graphics |date=2017-01-07 |website=Hardcore Gamer |access-date=2017-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170108093753/http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2017/01/07/best-of-2016-day-seven-ps-vita-3ds-artistic-design-technical-graphics/242164/ |archive-date=2017-01-08 |dead-url=no}}</ref>，获提名为[[IGN|IGN]]的年度最佳任天堂3DS和PlayStation Vita游戏<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/wikis/best-of-2016-awards/3DS_Game_of_the_Year |title=3DS Game of the Year |date=2017 |website=IGN |publisher=Ziff Davis |access-date=2017-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170112093642/http://www.ign.com/wikis/best-of-2016-awards/3DS_Game_of_the_Year |archive-date=2017-01-12 |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/wikis/best-of-2016-awards/PlayStation_Vita_Game_of_the_Year |title=PlayStation Vita Game of the Year |date=2017 |website=IGN |publisher=Ziff Davis |access-date=2017-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170112093853/http://www.ign.com/wikis/best-of-2016-awards/PlayStation_Vita_Game_of_the_Year |archive-date=2017-01-12 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏获两个RPGFan编辑选择奖，一个是彼得·特里森伯格（Peter Triezenberg）个人年度最佳游戏的第五位，一个是罗伯特·芬纳（Robert Fenner）最失望奖<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rpgfan.com/features/go2016/Editors_Awards/Robert_F.html |title=Robert Fenner's Awards |author=Fenner, Robert |date=2017 |work=RPGFan |access-date=2017-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170109023533/http://www.rpgfan.com/features/go2016/Editors_Awards/Robert_F.html |archive-date=2017-01-09 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。米拉入选[[Destructoid|Destructoid]]的2016年最受欢迎电子游戏角色<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.destructoid.com/good-golly-there-were-a-lot-of-great-new-characters-in-2016-406505.phtml |title=Good golly, there were a lot of great new characters in 2016 |author=Andriessen, CJ |date=2016-12-23 |website=Destructoid |publisher=Modern Method |access-date=2017-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170109183921/https://www.destructoid.com/good-golly-there-were-a-lot-of-great-new-characters-in-2016-406505.phtml |archive-date=2017-01-09 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

